<plot>In an exclusive interview, John Woo talks about his journey from Hong Kong to Hollywood - what inspired him to become a film-maker, his work as an editor for the Shaw Brothers, right through to establishing himself as one of America's most sought after Directors. Also interviewed are his long time producing partner, Terence Chang, and the cast of "Paycheck", Ben Affleck, Uma Thurman, Aaron Eckhart and Colm Feore.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?204946</url></doc>
